description.value: This value set pregnancy defines delivery and live birth procedures such as vaginal, cesarean and forcep deliveries. This grouping value set includes the value set Delivery and Live Births 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.12.1015 and Delivery Procedures 2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1078.5 which contains SNOMED CT, ICD10PCS codes Please see VSAC (https://vsac.nlm.nih.gov/) for the latest code expansion.

purpose.value: The purpose of this value set is to represent procedure concepts for single or multiple live deliveries.
